{"tid":2193213,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲老母係咁叫我去做全民檢測","createTime":"2020-09-07T15:47:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T10:41:43.000Z","uid":22796,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"207234d6e31c1ffea8d48d99b188444e6308d740","tid":2193213,"uid":22796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T15:47:34.000Z","msg":"我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    老母：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老母：你仲唔去做檢測？又唔洗好多時間又blablablablabla....<br />\n<br />\n我：測嚟做乜？有事就有事咖啦，你之前都話唔驚，美國流感每年都死幾千人，驚咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老母：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母班仆街藍絲KOL日撚日喺度宣傳<br />\n搞到我老母日撚日叫我去做<br />\n我今日頂唔順駁返佢<br />\n<br />\n你班藍絲KOL死全家好啦 咪撚累街坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4e6f83807354942d0c73f100564ffdd47f49ee","tid":2193213,"uid":309989,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T15:49:17.000Z","msg":"藍絲認為做咗等於免疫嘛！"},{"pid":"bb9cc9b7b36e88e13fcc85d7b2447c110d1c512e","tid":2193213,"uid":53612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T15:53:16.000Z","msg":"幾日貨仔<br />\n幾日驗一次咩<br />\n<br />\n又無口罩派"},{"pid":"fb2b8e15d89671e21385ca15250229a3d4188412","tid":2193213,"uid":22796,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T16:05:29.000Z","msg":"用藍絲論點駁藍絲其實幾好用<br />\n因為佢哋都唔識解畫<br />\n<br />\n班KOL一個大話冚一個大話<br />\n佢哋班授眾淨係吸收唔消化 到有人問起就hang機"},{"pid":"bdd8573494f0d8e68bfba9119d2115bda89d902e","tid":2193213,"uid":336090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T16:07:11.000Z","msg":"「吉完咽喉要補償，三個月比唔到家用」<br />\n佢即刻收聲"},{"pid":"3ae7a1ee1d0db2